<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<p>Solo İl Gala (“the App”) is developed by an independent developer. This Privacy Policy explains how the App collects, uses, and protects user information.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<p>The App does not collect personally identifiable information (PII).  
The App may collect non-personal analytics data such as device type, app version, and usage statistics.</p>

<h2>2. Third-Party Services</h2>
<p>The App may use the following third-party services:</p>
<ul>
<li>Google AdMob</li>
<li>Firebase Analytics</li>
<li>API-Football</li>
</ul>
<p>These services may collect data in accordance with their own privacy policies.</p>

<h2>3. Data Security</h2>
<p>We do not store any personal information on our own servers. Any data collected by third parties is protected under their security standards.</p>

<h2>4. User Rights</h2>
<p>Users may request deletion of any data stored by third-party providers by contacting them directly.</p>

<h2>5. Contact</h2>
<p>For questions or requests: burak.alkayaa@gmail.com</p>

